{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abafaf8f26","title":"复彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cde48a4bc8","index":0,"year":1949,"month":6,"day":11,"articleId":"abafaf8f26"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji26.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji26":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d81dca470e","type":"paragraph","text":"复彭德怀电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"abafaf8f26"},{"id":"8c3e4c1fb5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年6月11日）同意你的作战方针。作战时请注意先开灭宁马一个军，然后再好其一个军，各个击破，一次不要打多了[1]10日，彭怀电告毛泽东，认为如放齐在泾渭间作装，待6月底或7月兵力集中时再打胡、马，对我有诸多不利。如在泾济问作战，虽我现有兵力不占优势，但胡军士气很低，胡、马互信差，赫游山天然分割胡、马联系，有利我钳胡打马。我十八、十九兵团正向西安葡进，数日后我即稍占优","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"abafaf8f26"}],"page":{"id":"50fca32760","publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"abafaf8f26","start":470,"end":470}}}},"__N_SSG":true}